reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 26, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Solid Protection in a Slim Design - OTOFLY Soft Silicone iPhone 12/12 Pro Case Review
reviews.reviewText: The OTOFLY Soft Silicone iPhone 12/12 Pro Case has proven to be a reliable and durable option for protecting my precious device. Its blend of military-grade drop protection and slim, sleek design makes it an appealing choice for everyday use.The first thing that caught my attention was the stone color option. It offers a unique and stylish look that complements the sleek design of the iPhone 12/12 Pro perfectly. The soft silicone material feels smooth to the touch and provides a comfortable grip, making it easy to handle the phone without worrying about accidental slips.The military-grade drop protection is no exaggeration. This case has done an excellent job of safeguarding my phone from accidental drops and bumps. The raised edges around the screen and camera offer additional protection, ensuring that these vulnerable areas are shielded from direct impact.The microfiber lining inside the case is a thoughtful addition, preventing scratches on the phone's back and maintaining its pristine appearance. The snug fit of the case ensures that it stays in place securely without adding unnecessary bulk to the phone.The slim and thin design of the case is a standout feature for me. It maintains the phone's original form factor, making it easy to slide into pockets and bags without feeling overly bulky. This minimalist approach is something I appreciate, as I prefer cases that don't compromise the phone's slim profile.One minor drawback is that the soft silicone material can attract lint and dust over time, especially in darker color options like stone. Regular cleaning or using a lint roller can help keep the case looking clean and fresh.While this case offers good protection against everyday wear and tear, it may not be the best option for extreme outdoor activities or rugged environments. If you are someone who engages in rough outdoor activities frequently, you may want to consider a more heavy-duty case.Overall, the OTOFLY Soft Silicone iPhone 12/12 Pro Case strikes a balance between protection and style. It provides reliable drop protection while maintaining a slim and sleek appearance. The stone color option adds a touch of elegance to the phone, and the microfiber lining ensures that it stays scratch-free. For daily use and moderate protection, this case is an excellent choice, and I am pleased with my purchase. Four stars for a solid, well-designed protective phone case.
